<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vernal Swimming Lessons</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" href="logo.png" type="image/png">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <img class="logo" src="logo.png" alt="Logo">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/schedule">Schedule a Lesson</a></li>

                <% if (isLoggedIn) { %><li><a href="/account">My Lessons</a></li><% } %>

                <% if (isAdmin) { %>
                    <li><a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
                <% } %>
                <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
                    <li style="float:right"><a href="/logout">Log Out</a></li>
                <% } else { %>
                    <li style="float:right"><a href="/login">Log In</a></li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="intro">
            <h1>Swimming Lessons in Vernal, Utah</h1>
            <p>Any Age, Any Level! Swimming lessons taught by the best instructors in the Uintah Basin at affordable rates. Sign-up today so that your child can learn to swim like a fish from a friendly, positive, and encouraging instructor.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="instructor">
            <h2>Our Instructor</h2>
            <img class="instructor-portrait" src="john_batty_cropped.jpg" alt="John Batty, Advanced Swimming Instructor" width="200px" >
            <h3 style="font-size: 26px; text-align: left;">John Batty</h3>
            <p style="text-align: left;">John has been teaching swimming lessons for over 10 years! John has taught thousands of students of ages ranging from 6 months to 64 years, and every skill level from a child’s first time in the water to athlete’s earning college scholarships for swimming.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Vernal Swimming Lessons</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
